==About==
===Format===
* '''IN-Game Qualifiers:''''' Jun 26th - 30th, 2026
* '''Round 1:''''' July 6th - 9th, 2026
** 1024 Teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams divided into 64 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 3 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 4 Teams}} from each group (Total 256 Teams) qualify for ''Round 2.

* '''Round 2:''''' July 11th - 13th, 2026
** 256 Teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 16 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 9 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 2 Teams}} from each group (Total 32 Teams) qualify for ''Semi Finals.

* '''Semi Finals:''''' July 18th - 21st, 2026
** 32 Teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups with 8 Teams in each group.
** Single Round-robin format.
** Each team plays a total of 12 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 Teams}} advance to ''Grand Finals.

* '''Grand Finals:''''' July 24th - 26th, 2026
** 16 Teams, 3 matchdays.
** 18 matches (6 each day).

